ecj1jnbKvC802QZ8","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recO90vwNl73z9r2r","target":"rec3MVp8Zrl05FzwF","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recO90vwNl73z9r2r","target":"recM30yMa9NH5DOVq","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recO90vwNl73z9r2r","target":"recpqKANUDcRgN4HU","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recO90vwNl73z9r2r","target":"recL1WV82pXaRBQ59","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recO90vwNl73z9r2r","target":"recOpGyXVzzKCuVs5","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recO90vwNl73z9r2r","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recO90vwNl73z9r2r","target":"recBsRcVlu8hkiGKW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recO90vwNl73z9r2r","target":"recsX4et9ux7g07Zg","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recO90vwNl73z9r2r","target":"rec5pDuWtEaOK7ehk","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recdyTKDd8CiuhhGg","ref":"Jer.32.1","text":"The word that came to Jeremiah from the LORD in the tenth year of Zedekiah king of Judah, which was the eighteenth year of Nebuchadrezzar.","year":-589},{"id":"recwmaWS0gry0zQNU","ref":"Jer.32.2","text":"For then the king of Babylon’s army besieged Jerusalem: and Jeremiah the prophet was shut up in the court of the prison, which was in the king of Judah’s house.","year":-589},{"id":"recQFJdRAxnBjardW","ref":"Jer.32.3","text":"For Zedekiah king of Judah had shut him up, saying, Wherefore dost thou prophesy, and say, Thus saith the LORD, Behold, I will give this city into the hand of the king of Babylon, and he shall take it;","year":-589},{"id":"recKdURf01Toz4H4C","ref":"Jer.32.4","text":"And Zedekiah king of Judah shall not escape out of the hand of the Chaldeans, but shall surely be delivered into the hand of the king of Babylon, and shall speak with him mouth to mouth, and his eyes shall behold his eyes;","year":-589},{"id":"recgxkBFYMs5bYuhn","ref":"Jer.32.5","text":"And he shall lead Zedekiah to Babylon, and there shall he be until I visit him, saith the LORD: though ye fight with the Chaldeans, ye shall not prosper.","year":-589},{"id":"reckfqs8v52NqAt1I","ref":"Jer.32.6","text":"And Jeremiah said, The word of the LORD came unto me, saying,","year":-589},{"id":"rec4rpPj8OYzGJaNQ","ref":"Jer.32.7","text":"Behold, Hanameel the son of Shallum thine uncle shall come unto thee, saying, Buy thee my field that is in Anathoth: for the right of redemption is thine to buy it.","year":-589},{"id":"recylP1GoQE3MYgRS","ref":"Jer.32.8","text":"So Hanameel mine uncle’s son came to me in the court of the prison according to the word of the LORD, and said unto me, Buy my field, I pray thee, that is in Anathoth, which is in the country of Benjamin: for the right of inheritance is thine, and the redemption is thine; buy it for thyself. Then I knew that this was the word of the LORD.","year":-589}]}
